moji\" /><br />\n同埋好肯定如果佢最後得到 <br />\n好大機會唔珍惜 <br />\n但你唔捨得既話 如果佢之後傾完態度有變 真係尊重你既 都有得諗下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:13:25.000Z","msg":"sorry唔小心hi到負皮<br />\n<br />\n但係你真係講得好啱 其實處唔處呢家嘢 你自己決定㗎姐 鍾意俾邊個咪邊個 <br />\n<br />\n不過係咪真係要俾一個唔尊重你嘅男人 唔俾佢屌佢就嬲嘅男人 隨時中出即飛嘅男人 呢樣你就自己諗啦<br />\n<br />\n其實樓主你自己都有答案啦 諗清楚啦 加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1250e85e93e82f3eda5f0d334327ab4dded86fee","tid":1128442,"uid":74462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:36:26.000Z","msg":"連登仔唔係話唔畀扑嘅女即飛？？"},{"pid":"9b57fb171b2906f3593be6528df49e4481d9f1ff","tid":1128442,"uid":216760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0c4f2c2df2eebd18af0062da95b5825d8842d0f","tid":1128442,"uid":244634,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"quote":{"pid":"1b3501e38aa7c6be04224758a10369ebe7b5a235","tid":1128442,"uid":125966,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T22:30:57.000Z","msg":"未一齊之前係咪已經知你係處？<br />\n你都講到出口佢竟然嬲 一定唔會係愛<br />\n諗清楚呀絲打 未好深既時候好抽身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T22:35:07.000Z","msg":"未一齊之前唔知呀<br />\n其實我都好亂 唔知自己想點<br />\n雖然佢係咁 但我又會諗返佢對我好既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:36:50.000Z","msg":"佢對你既好有冇目的？<br />\n睇下幾個月得唔到佢想要既 係唔係仲對你咁好"},{"pid":"6a66d6e9767dca357fe38f602b107b0808e40b7e","tid":1128442,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:37:22.000Z","msg":"唔同concept都可以拍到拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de31e3b25402f34eae60ffb885d16708404e1a2","tid":1128442,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-28T04:37:53.000Z","msg":"飛7佢，鍾意你既人係尊重你。"},{"pid":"c449ed38d589db0b0e5e91a88614c452a56aab1f","tid":1128442,"uid":124584,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1f9c0e4ece4bd5356888226194d478bc293360ae","tid":1128442,"uid":244634,"l